points.title: This service does not track you
points.status: The privacy policy states plainly that it does not track you in any way, shape, or form. There are no plugins, no javascript tracking, no server side tracking.
points.quoteText:
This website, livearchivist.com, does not track you in any way, shape, or form.

I do not use tracking.

I do not use analytics.

I do not use any javascript.
